      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true,
      "clearStorySprites": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――昼休憩の時間。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "休憩室には、いつものようにココアの香りが残っていた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "白いマグカップと黒いマグカップがテーブルに並び、その横に、店長用の湯飲みも置かれている。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "店長、ココアじゃなくてお茶でよかったですか？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ああ。\n今日はお茶で大丈夫。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "大丈夫って言った。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "……言ったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "すぐ大丈夫って言う。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空、今日も店長のこと見てるね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "見てない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "見てるよ。\nさっきも、店長が棚の上の商品を取ろうとした時、すぐそっち見てた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "見てない。\n視界に入っただけ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空、俺はもう普通に動けるぞ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "普通に動ける人は、棚の上の商品を取る時に一瞬だけ肩を気にしない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "よく見てるな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "見てないって言った。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ふふっ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空も笑わないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ごめん。\nでも、夜空が店長を心配してるの、少し安心するから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "安心しなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "安心したいからするの。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……まっすぐすぎる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空は考えすぎ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "何回でも言うね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "何回でも言うよ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は黒いマグカップを手に取る。\nけれど飲むより先に、また店長の方を見た。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "本当に大丈夫だ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "その言葉が信用できない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "困ったな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "困って。\n店長は自分のことをすぐ後回しにする。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
