        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "数段だ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "数段でも落ちた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "まあ、それはそうだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "だから、しばらくは無理しないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "わかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "重いものを持たないで。\n高いところの商品を取らないで。\n走らないで。\nあと、変に我慢しないで。",
