          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "もし、店長に何かあったら。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ぼくが、責任を取る。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "どうやって？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "通院が必要なら付き添う。\n荷物が持てないなら持つ。\n仕事ができないなら手伝う。\n生活に支障が出るなら……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "出るなら？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……ぼくが、一生面倒を見る。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "……一生？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "あ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "はは、まるでプロポーズか介護宣言だな……。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ぷろぽーず……？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……っ！？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空の表情が、一瞬で固まった。\n自分の言葉と、店長の言葉が、少し遅れて頭の中でつながったようだった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ち、違う！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "違うのか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "違う！\nそういう意味じゃない！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "じゃあ、介護宣言の方か？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そっちでもない！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "……ふふ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空も……っていうか、何で少し笑ってるの！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね。\n笑うところじゃないのは、わかってるんだけど。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "じゃあ、笑わないで！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "うん。\nでも、夜空がすごく真剣に店長のことを考えてたのがわかって……少し安心しちゃって。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "安心するところじゃない！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "俺も少し安心した。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "店長も乗らないで！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪い。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "謝らないで！\n余計に変になる！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空、顔真っ赤だよ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなくていい！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は両手でマグカップを包む。\n飲もうとして、熱さに気づいて、結局飲まずに戻した。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "違う。\n違うから。\n一生っていうのは、責任期間の話で。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "責任期間。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そう。\nつまり、後遺症が残った場合の長期的な支援というか。\n生活補助とか、通院補助とか、業務補助とか。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "介助まで考えてたのか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "人が真剣に悩んでるのに！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "いや、真剣なのはわかってる。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "わかってない。\n店長は絶対わかってない。\n今、ちょっと変な意味で聞いた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "少しだけ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "認めないで！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "店長、今のは店長も少し悪いです。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪かった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空、味方しなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "味方だよ？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そういうまっすぐなのも今はやめて。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そもそも、店長が悪い。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "俺か？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そう。\n大丈夫ってすぐ言うから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それで一生面倒を見る話になるのか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わないで！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪い。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "それに、店長がちゃんと病院に行くって言えば、ぼくもここまで考えない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "必要なら行くとは言った。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "必要の判断が甘い。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "そうか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "甘い。\n美空のココアより甘い。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "わたしのココア、そこまで甘くないよ？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "甘い。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "控えめにしてるのに。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "甘い。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "じゃあ、次はもっと控えめ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "今その話じゃない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ごめん。\nでも、少し戻ってきたかなって。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "何が。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "いつもの夜空。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空らしいな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "店長も言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪い。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……でも、今のはぎりぎり。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "許されたか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ぎりぎり。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空はようやくココアを一口飲む。\n甘さ控えめのはずなのに、やっぱり少し甘い。\nそれが少しだけ落ち着かなくて、少しだけ落ち着いた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "なに。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "店長のこと、大事なんだね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "美空。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。\nでも、そう思ったから。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……責任。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "うん。\n今はそういうことにしておくね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そういうことにしておく、じゃなくて、そういうこと。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は顔をそらす。\nけれど、さっきまでのような重い沈黙ではなかった。\n恥ずかしさと、怒りと、少しだけいつもの調子。\nその全部が混ざって、休憩室の空気を少しだけ軽くしていた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "なに。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "本当に痛かったら言う。\n我慢もしない。\n高いところの商品も、しばらくは他の人に頼む。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "本当に？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "本当に。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……なら、ぎりぎり。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ぎりぎり多いな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "店長は、ぎりぎりのところにいすぎ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "気をつける。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そうして。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空はもう一口、ココアを飲む。\n今度は少しだけ、表情が緩んだ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空、ココアどう？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "甘い。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "やっぱり？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "うん。\nでも、今日はそれでいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "そっか。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "うん。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "でも、今日はいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――休憩時間の終わりを知らせるチャイムが、店内の奥で小さく鳴った。\n夜空はマグカップを置き、店長を見る。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "店長。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ん？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "本当に痛くなったら、言って。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "言う。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなかったら、怒る。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "わかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "あと、一生面倒を見るとかは……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "忘れて。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "努力する。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "信用できない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "少しだけなら？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……少しだけなら。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "じゃあ、少しだけ覚えておく。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そういうところ！",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ふふっ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空まで笑わないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空はそう言って、休憩室を出る。\n足取りはまだ少しだけぎこちない。\nけれど、昨日までのように重く沈んだものではなかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――店長のことが心配。\nそれをまだ、夜空は「責任」と呼ぶ。\nけれど、その言葉の奥に別の温度があることを、美空は少しだけ気づいていた。"
    }
  ],
